<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='980000' id='t-980000'>It's unfortunate that they tend to be selectively deployed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='985000' id='t-985000'>And it's going to take real work to change that.</span>
